
## (Developer Reference Notes)**

# =========================================================
# QUICK REFERENCE - RENDER DEPLOY TRIGGER COMMAND
# =========================================================
# Purpose:
# Manually trigger a Render deployment from the command line
# using your service ID and API key.
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Usage:
# 1. Replace rnd_xxxx with your RENDER_API_KEY
# 2. Replace srv-xxxx with your RENDER_SERVICE_ID
# 3. Run in your terminal to manually trigger deployment

curl -X POST \
  -H "Accept: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer rnd_xxxx" \
  -d '{"serviceId":"srv-xxxx"}' \
  https://api.render.com/v1/services/srv-xxxx/deploys
